  "title": "Steel-Edged Sakura",
  "description": "The war with the undead started eighteen years ago, but the history of her clan stretches much, much further. Though her village was little more than a farming settlement by the time it fell, it guarded an ancient samurai fortress. The last lord to reside in that fortress met his death at the hands of the undead. Now, like everything else, it sits abandoned.\n\nShiori has never set foot inside it herself. As bodyguards of the samurai, her family was not permitted within its walls without their master's blessing.\n\nBut sometimes in her dreams, she travels to its gates to stand watch.",
